msgstr "書式: <option>--split</option> <literal>timestamps:</literal><parameter>A</parameter><optional>,<parameter>B</parameter><optional>,<parameter>C</parameter>...</optional></optional>"

#. type: Content of: <refentry><refsect1><refsect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para><orderedlist><listitem><para>
